posting_body: ['YES, WE ARE OPEN!', 'CALL NOW TO SCHEDULE AN IN-PERSON TOUR!', 'OR LET US SHOW YOU THROUGH FACETIME!', 'Welcome to Boulders at Puget Sound, conveniently located in North Tacoma, WA near Route 16, I-705 and I-5.', 'At Boulders at Puget Sound, we pride ourselves on providing the best apartment living that Tacoma has to offer.', 'Choose from our selection of one, two, and three-bedroom apartments - here, every layout was designed to meet all of your apartment needs.', 'Convinced Boulders at Puget Sound is the right Tacoma apartment for you?', 'Apply online today!', ' APARTMENTS IN TACOMA, WA WITH UNMATCHED AMENITIES', 'Amenities Include:', 'Granite Countertops', 'Community Clubhouse', 'Fireplace', 'Spacious Walk-in Closets', 'In-Unit Laundry', 'Ground-Level, Private Entries', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Swimming Pool', 'Dog Park', 'Abundant Natural Light', 'Extra Storage', 'Dishwasher', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
